{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Walk around for four months with three wishes,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and all the ideas will start to percolate up."},{"time":7000,"text":"I think everybody should do it -- think that you've got three wishes."},{"time":9000,"text":"And what would you do? It's actually a great exercise"},{"time":11000,"text":"to really drill down to the things that you feel are important,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and really reflect on the world around us."},{"time":19000,"text":"And thinking that, can an individual actually do something,"},{"time":23000,"text":"or come up with something,"},{"time":25000,"text":"that may actually get some traction out there and make a difference?"},{"time":29000,"text":"Inspired by nature -- that's the theme here."},{"time":33000,"text":"And I think, quite frankly, that's where I started."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"I became very interested in the landscape as a Canadian."},{"time":43000,"text":"We have this Great North. And there was a pretty small population,"},{"time":46000,"text":"and my father was an avid outdoorsman."},{"time":48000,"text":"So I really had a chance to experience that."},{"time":51000,"text":"And I could never really understand exactly what it was, or how it was informing me."},{"time":55000,"text":"But what I think it was telling me"},{"time":57000,"text":"is that we are this transient thing that's happening,"},{"time":62000,"text":"and that the nature that you see out there -- the untouched shorelines,"},{"time":66000,"text":"the untouched forest that I was able to see --"},{"time":69000,"text":"really bring in a sense of that geological time,"},{"time":76000,"text":"that this has gone on for a long time,"},{"time":78000,"text":"and we're experiencing it in a different way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"And that, to me, was a reference point that I think I needed to have"},{"time":87000,"text":"to be able to make the work that I did."},{"time":89000,"text":"And I did go out, and I did this picture of grasses coming through in the spring,"},{"time":94000,"text":"along a roadside."},{"time":96000,"text":"This rebirth of grass. And then I went out for years"},{"time":99000,"text":"trying to photograph the pristine landscape."},{"time":102000,"text":"But as a fine-art photographer I somehow felt"},{"time":105000,"text":"that it wouldn't catch on out there,"},{"time":107000,"text":"that there would be a problem with trying to make this as a fine-art career."},{"time":111000,"text":"And I kept being sucked into this genre of the calendar picture,"},{"time":116000,"text":"or something of that nature, and I couldn't get away from it."},{"time":118000,"text":"So I started to think of, how can I rethink the landscape?"},{"time":122000,"text":"I decided to rethink the landscape"},{"time":124000,"text":"as the landscape that we've transformed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"I had a bit of an epiphany being lost in Pennsylvania,"},{"time":129000,"text":"and I took a left turn trying to get back to the highway."},{"time":133000,"text":"And I ended up in a town called Frackville."},{"time":135000,"text":"I got out of the car, and I stood up,"},{"time":137000,"text":"and it was a coal-mining town. I did a 360 turnaround,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and that became one of the most surreal landscapes I've ever seen."},{"time":145000,"text":"Totally transformed by man."},{"time":148000,"text":"And that got me to go out and look at mines like this,"},{"time":151000,"text":"and go out and look at the largest industrial incursions"},{"time":154000,"text":"in the landscape that I could find."},{"time":156000,"text":"And that became the baseline of what I was doing."},{"time":159000,"text":"And it also became the theme that I felt that I could hold onto,"},{"time":164000,"text":"and not have to re-invent myself --"},{"time":166000,"text":"that this theme was large enough to become a life's work,"},{"time":169000,"text":"to become something that I could sink my teeth into"},{"time":173000,"text":"and just research and find out where these industries are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"And I think one of the things I also wanted to say in my thanks,"},{"time":180000,"text":"which I kind of missed,"},{"time":182000,"text":"was to thank all the corporations who helped me get in."},{"time":185000,"text":"Because it took negotiation for almost every one of these photographs --"},{"time":189000,"text":"to get into that place to make those photographs,"},{"time":193000,"text":"and if it wasn't for those people letting me in"},{"time":196000,"text":"at the heads of those corporations,"},{"time":198000,"text":"I would have never made this body of work."},{"time":200000,"text":"So in that respect, to me, I'm not against the corporation."},{"time":205000,"text":"I own a corporation. I work with them,"},{"time":208000,"text":"and I feel that we all need them and they're important."},{"time":211000,"text":"But I am also for sustainability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"So there's this thing that is pulling me in both directions."},{"time":216000,"text":"And I'm not making an indictment towards what's happening here,"},{"time":220000,"text":"but it is a slow progression."},{"time":222000,"text":"So I started thinking, well, we live in all these ages of man:"},{"time":225000,"text":"the Stone Age, and the Iron Age, and the Copper Age."},{"time":229000,"text":"And these ages of man are still at work today."},{"time":233000,"text":"But we've become totally disconnected from them."},{"time":235000,"text":"There's something that we're not seeing there."},{"time":238000,"text":"And it's a scary thing as well. Because when we start looking"},{"time":242000,"text":"at the collective appetite for our lifestyles,"},{"time":245000,"text":"and what we're doing to that landscape --"},{"time":248000,"text":"that, to me, is something that is a very sobering moment for me to contemplate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254000,"text":"And through my photographs,"},{"time":256000,"text":"I'm hoping to be able to engage the audiences of my work,"},{"time":262000,"text":"and to come up to it and not immediately be rejected by the image."},{"time":265000,"text":"Not to say, \"Oh my God, what is it?\" but to be challenged by it --"},{"time":268000,"text":"to say, \"Wow, this is beautiful,\" on one level,"},{"time":270000,"text":"but on the other level, \"This is scary. I shouldn't be enjoying it.\""},{"time":274000,"text":"Like a forbidden pleasure. And it's that forbidden pleasure"},{"time":277000,"text":"that I think is what resonates out there,"},{"time":279000,"text":"and it gets people to look at these things,"},{"time":281000,"text":"and it gets people to enter it. And it also, in a way, defines kind of what I feel, too --"},{"time":288000,"text":"that I'm drawn to have a good life."},{"time":291000,"text":"I want a house, and I want a car."},{"time":293000,"text":"But there's this consequence out there."},{"time":295000,"text":"And how do I begin to have that attraction, repulsion?"},{"time":298000,"text":"It's even in my own conscience I'm having it,"},{"time":301000,"text":"and here in my work, I'm trying to build that same toggle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305000,"text":"These things that I photographed -- this tire pile here"},{"time":308000,"text":"had 45 million tires in it. It was the largest one."},{"time":311000,"text":"It was only about an hour-and-a-half away from me, and it caught fire"},{"time":314000,"text":"about four years ago. It's around Westley, California, around Modesto."},{"time":318000,"text":"And I decided to start looking at something that, to me, had --"},{"time":322000,"text":"if the earlier work of looking at the landscape"},{"time":324000,"text":"had a sense of lament to what we were doing to nature,"},{"time":327000,"text":"in the recycling work that you're seeing here"},{"time":330000,"text":"was starting to point to a direction. To me, it was our redemption."},{"time":334000,"text":"That in the recycling work that I was doing,"},{"time":336000,"text":"I'm looking for a practice, a human activity that is sustainable."},{"time":343000,"text":"That if we keep putting things, through industrial and urban existence,"},{"time":348000,"text":"back into the system --"},{"time":350000,"text":"if we keep doing that -- we can continue on."},{"time":353000,"text":"Of course, listening at the conference,"},{"time":355000,"text":"there's many, many things that are coming. Bio-mimicry,"},{"time":358000,"text":"and there's many other things that are coming on stream --"},{"time":360000,"text":"nanotechnology that may also prevent us from having"},{"time":365000,"text":"to go into that landscape and tear it apart."},{"time":368000,"text":"And we all look forward to those things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"But in the meantime, these things are scaling up."},{"time":372000,"text":"These things are continuing to happen."},{"time":374000,"text":"What you're looking at here -- I went to Bangladesh,"},{"time":377000,"text":"so I started to move away from North America;"},{"time":380000,"text":"I started to look at our world globally."},{"time":382000,"text":"These images of Bangladesh"},{"time":384000,"text":"came out of a radio program I was listening to."},{"time":387000,"text":"They were talking about Exxon Valdez,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and that there was going to be a glut of oil tankers"},{"time":392000,"text":"because of the insurance industries."},{"time":394000,"text":"And that those oil tankers needed to be decommissioned,"},{"time":396000,"text":"and 2004 was going to be the pinnacle."},{"time":398000,"text":"And I thought, \"My God, wouldn't that be something?\""},{"time":400000,"text":"To see the largest vessels of man being deconstructed by hand,"},{"time":404000,"text":"literally, in third-world countries."},{"time":406000,"text":"So originally I was going to go to India."},{"time":408000,"text":"And I was shut out of India because of a Greenpeace situation there,"},{"time":411000,"text":"and then I was able to get into Bangladesh,"},{"time":413000,"text":"and saw for the first time a third world, a view of it,"},{"time":418000,"text":"that I had never actually thought was possible."},{"time":422000,"text":"130 million people living in an area the size of Wisconsin --"},{"time":425000,"text":"people everywhere -- the pollution was intense,"},{"time":428000,"text":"and the working conditions were horrible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431000,"text":"Here you're looking at some oil fields in California,"},{"time":433000,"text":"some of the biggest oil fields. And again, I started to think that --"},{"time":438000,"text":"there was another epiphany --"},{"time":441000,"text":"that the whole world I was living in was"},{"time":443000,"text":"a result of having plentiful oil."},{"time":446000,"text":"And that, to me, was again something that I started building on,"},{"time":450000,"text":"and I continued to build on."},{"time":452000,"text":"So this is a series I'm hoping to have ready"},{"time":456000,"text":"in about two or three years,"},{"time":458000,"text":"under the heading of \"The Oil Party.\""},{"time":460000,"text":"Because I think everything that we're involved in --"},{"time":462000,"text":"our clothing, our cars, our roads, and everything -- are directly a result."},{"time":466000,"text":"I'm going to move to some pictures of China."},{"time":471000,"text":"And for me China -- I started photographing it four years ago,"},{"time":474000,"text":"and China truly is a question of sustainability in my mind,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"not to mention that China, as well,"},{"time":480000,"text":"has a great effect on the industries that I grew up around."},{"time":483000,"text":"I came out of a blue-collar town,"},{"time":485000,"text":"a GM town, and my father worked at GM,"},{"time":488000,"text":"so I was very familiar with that kind of industry"},{"time":492000,"text":"and that also informed my work. But you know,"},{"time":497000,"text":"to see China and the scale at which it's evolving, is quite something."},{"time":503000,"text":"So what you see here is the Three Gorges Dam,"},{"time":506000,"text":"and this is the largest dam by 50 percent ever attempted by man."},{"time":511000,"text":"Most of the engineers around the world left the project"},{"time":515000,"text":"because they said, \"It's just too big.\""},{"time":517000,"text":"In fact, when it did actually fill with water a year and a half ago,"},{"time":521000,"text":"they were able to measure a wobble within the earth as it was spinning."},{"time":524000,"text":"It took fifteen days to fill it."},{"time":526000,"text":"So this created a reservoir 600 kilometers long,"},{"time":531000,"text":"one of the largest reservoirs ever created."},{"time":533000,"text":"And what was also one of the bigger projects around that"},{"time":538000,"text":"was moving 13 full-size cities up out of the reservoir,"},{"time":542000,"text":"and flattening all the buildings so they could make way for the ships."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545000,"text":"This is a \"before and after.\" So that was before."},{"time":549000,"text":"And this is like 10 weeks later, demolished by hand."},{"time":552000,"text":"I think 11 of the buildings they used dynamite,"},{"time":554000,"text":"everything else was by hand. That was 10 weeks later."},{"time":556000,"text":"And this gives you an idea."},{"time":558000,"text":"And it was all the people who lived in those homes,"},{"time":561000,"text":"were the ones that were actually taking it apart"},{"time":563000,"text":"and working, and getting paid per brick to take their cities apart."},{"time":568000,"text":"And these are some of the images from that."},{"time":570000,"text":"So I spent about three trips to the Three Gorges Dam,"},{"time":573000,"text":"looking at that massive transformation of a landscape."},{"time":577000,"text":"And it looks like a bombed-out landscape, but it isn't."},{"time":580000,"text":"What it is, it's a landscape that is an intentional one."},{"time":584000,"text":"This is a need for power, and they're willing to go through this"},{"time":589000,"text":"massive transformation, on this scale, to get that power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596000,"text":"And again, it's actually a relief for what's going on in China"},{"time":602000,"text":"because I think on the table right now,"},{"time":604000,"text":"there's 27 nuclear power stations to be built."},{"time":607000,"text":"There hasn't been one built in North America for 20 years"},{"time":609000,"text":"because of the \"NIMBY\" problem -- \"Not In My BackYard.\""},{"time":611000,"text":"But in China they're saying, \"No, we're putting in 27 in the next 10 years.\""},{"time":614000,"text":"And coal-burning furnaces are going in there"},{"time":618000,"text":"for hydroelectric power literally weekly."},{"time":621000,"text":"So coal itself is probably one of the largest problems."},{"time":626000,"text":"And one of the other things that happened in the Three Gorges --"},{"time":628000,"text":"a lot of the agricultural land that you see there on the left was also lost;"},{"time":633000,"text":"some of the most fertile agricultural land was lost in that."},{"time":636000,"text":"And 1.2 to 2 million people were relocated,"},{"time":639000,"text":"depending on whose statistics you're looking at."},{"time":642000,"text":"And this is what they were building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644000,"text":"This is Wushan, one of the largest cities that was relocated."},{"time":648000,"text":"This is the town hall for the city."},{"time":651000,"text":"And again, the rebuilding of the city -- to me, it was sad to see"},{"time":656000,"text":"that they didn't really grab a lot of, I guess,"},{"time":658000,"text":"what we know here, in terms of urban planning."},{"time":661000,"text":"There were no parks; there were no green spaces."},{"time":664000,"text":"Very high-density living on the side of a hill."},{"time":667000,"text":"And here they had a chance to rebuild cities from the bottom up,"},{"time":670000,"text":"but somehow were not connecting with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673000,"text":"Here is a sign that, translated, says, \"Obey the birth control law."},{"time":678000,"text":"Build our science, civilized and advanced idea of marriage and giving birth.\""},{"time":682000,"text":"So here, if you look at this poster,"},{"time":685000,"text":"it has all the trappings of Western culture."},{"time":688000,"text":"You're seeing the tuxedos, the bouquets."},{"time":692000,"text":"But what's really, to me, frightening about the picture"},{"time":695000,"text":"and about this billboard is the refinery in the background."},{"time":698000,"text":"So it's like marrying up all the things that we have"},{"time":701000,"text":"and it's an adaptation of our way of life, full stop."},{"time":707000,"text":"And again, when you start seeing that kind of embrace,"},{"time":713000,"text":"and you start looking at them leading their rural lifestyle"},{"time":717000,"text":"with a very, very small footprint and moving into an urban lifestyle"},{"time":722000,"text":"with a much higher footprint, it starts to become very sobering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725000,"text":"This is a shot in one of the biggest squares in Guangdong --"},{"time":728000,"text":"and this is where a lot of migrant workers are coming in from the country."},{"time":733000,"text":"And there's about 130 million people in migration"},{"time":736000,"text":"trying to get into urban centers at all times,"},{"time":738000,"text":"and in the next 10 to 15 years, are expecting"},{"time":742000,"text":"another 400 to 500 million people to migrate"},{"time":745000,"text":"into the urban centers like Shanghai and the manufacturing centers."},{"time":750000,"text":"The manufacturers are --"},{"time":752000,"text":"the domestics are usually -- you can tell a domestic factory by the fact"},{"time":756000,"text":"that they all use the same color uniforms."},{"time":759000,"text":"So this is a pink uniform at this factory. It's a shoe factory."},{"time":762000,"text":"And they have dorms for the workers."},{"time":764000,"text":"So they bring them in from the country and put them up in the dorms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767000,"text":"This is one of the biggest shoe factories, the Yuyuan shoe factory"},{"time":771000,"text":"near Shenzhen. It has 90,000 employees making shoes."},{"time":776000,"text":"This is a shift change, one of three."},{"time":779000,"text":"There's two factories of this scale in the same town."},{"time":782000,"text":"This is one with 45,000, so every lunch,"},{"time":785000,"text":"there's about 12,000 coming through for lunch."},{"time":787000,"text":"They sit down; they have about 20 minutes."},{"time":789000,"text":"The next round comes in. It's an incredible workforce"},{"time":792000,"text":"that's building there. Shanghai --"},{"time":795000,"text":"I'm looking at the urban renewal in Shanghai,"},{"time":798000,"text":"and this is a whole area that will be flattened"},{"time":800000,"text":"and turned into skyscrapers in the next five years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805000,"text":"What's also happening in Shanghai is --"},{"time":807000,"text":"China is changing because this wouldn't have happened"},{"time":811000,"text":"five years ago, for instance. This is a holdout."},{"time":813000,"text":"They're called dengzahoos -- they're like pin tacks to the ground."},{"time":816000,"text":"They won't move. They're not negotiating."},{"time":818000,"text":"They're not getting enough, so they're not going to move."},{"time":821000,"text":"And so they're holding off until they get a deal with them."},{"time":824000,"text":"And they've been actually quite successful in getting better deals"},{"time":827000,"text":"because most of them are getting a raw deal."},{"time":829000,"text":"They're being put out about two hours --"},{"time":831000,"text":"the communities that have been around for literally hundreds of years,"},{"time":834000,"text":"or maybe even thousands of years,"},{"time":836000,"text":"are being broken up and spread across in the suburban areas"},{"time":839000,"text":"outside of Shanghai. But these are a whole series of guys"},{"time":842000,"text":"holding out in this reconstruction of Shanghai."},{"time":847000,"text":"Probably the largest urban-renewal project, I think,"},{"time":851000,"text":"ever attempted on the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"And then the embrace of the things that they're replacing it with --"},{"time":857000,"text":"again, one of my wishes, and I never ended up going there,"},{"time":860000,"text":"was to somehow tell them that there were better ways to build a house."},{"time":863000,"text":"The kinds of collisions of styles and things were quite something,"},{"time":869000,"text":"and these are called the villas."},{"time":873000,"text":"And also, like right now, they're just moving."},{"time":876000,"text":"The scaffolding is still on, and this is an e-waste area,"},{"time":880000,"text":"and if you looked in the foreground on the big print,"},{"time":882000,"text":"you'd see that the industry -- their industry -- they're all recycling."},{"time":885000,"text":"So the industry's already growing"},{"time":887000,"text":"around these new developments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890000,"text":"This is a five-level bridge in Shanghai."},{"time":892000,"text":"Shanghai was a very intriguing city -- it's exploding on a level"},{"time":898000,"text":"that I don't think any city has experienced."},{"time":902000,"text":"In fact, even Shenzhen, the economic zone --"},{"time":907000,"text":"one of the first ones -- 15 years ago was about 100,000 people,"},{"time":912000,"text":"and today it boasts about 10 to 11 million."},{"time":915000,"text":"So that gives you an idea of the kinds of migrations and the speed with which --"},{"time":920000,"text":"this is just the taxis being built by Volkswagen."},{"time":923000,"text":"There's 9,000 of them here,"},{"time":926000,"text":"and they're being built for most of the big cities,"},{"time":930000,"text":"Beijing and Shanghai, Shenzhen."},{"time":933000,"text":"And this isn't even the domestic car market; this is the taxi market."},{"time":942000,"text":"And what we would see here as a suburban development --"},{"time":947000,"text":"a similar thing, but they're all high-rises."},{"time":950000,"text":"So they'll put 20 or 40 up at a time,"},{"time":952000,"text":"and they just go up in the same way"},{"time":954000,"text":"as a single-family dwelling would go up here in an area."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"And the density is quite incredible."},{"time":964000,"text":"And one of the things in this picture that I wanted to point out"},{"time":971000,"text":"is that when I saw these kinds of buildings,"},{"time":974000,"text":"I was shocked to see"},{"time":976000,"text":"that they're not using a central air-conditioning system;"},{"time":980000,"text":"every window has an air conditioner in it."},{"time":983000,"text":"And I'm sure there are people here who probably"},{"time":986000,"text":"know better than I do about efficiencies,"},{"time":988000,"text":"but I can't imagine that every apartment having its own air conditioner"},{"time":992000,"text":"is a very efficient way to cool a building on this scale."},{"time":994000,"text":"And when you start looking at that,"},{"time":996000,"text":"and then you start factoring up into a city the size of Shanghai,"},{"time":1001000,"text":"it's literally a forest of skyscrapers."},{"time":1004000,"text":"It's breathtaking, in terms of the speed at which this city is transforming."},{"time":1010000,"text":"And you can see in the foreground of this picture,"},{"time":1012000,"text":"it's still one of the last areas that was being held up."},{"time":1015000,"text":"Right now that's all cleared out -- this was done about eight months ago --"},{"time":1018000,"text":"and high-rises are now going up into that central spot."},{"time":1021000,"text":"So a skyscraper is built, literally, overnight in Shanghai."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1030000,"text":"Most recently I went in, and I started looking"},{"time":1032000,"text":"at some of the biggest industries in China."},{"time":1035000,"text":"And this is Baosteel, right outside of Shanghai."},{"time":1039000,"text":"This is the coal supply for the steel factory -- 18 square kilometers."},{"time":1044000,"text":"It's an incredibly massive operation, I think 15,000 workers,"},{"time":1051000,"text":"five cupolas, and the sixth one's coming in here."},{"time":1055000,"text":"So they're building very large blast furnaces"},{"time":1060000,"text":"to try to deal with the demand for steel in China."},{"time":1064000,"text":"So this is three of the visible blast furnaces within that shot."},{"time":1069000,"text":"And again, looking at these images, there's this constant, like, haze that you're seeing."},{"time":1075000,"text":"This is going to show you, real time, an assembler. It's a circuit breaker."},{"time":1094000,"text":"10 hours a day at this speed."},{"time":1108000,"text":"I think one of the issues"},{"time":1114000,"text":"that we here are facing with China,"},{"time":1119000,"text":"is that they're using a lot of the latest production technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1122000,"text":"In that one, there were 400 people that worked on the floor."},{"time":1125000,"text":"And I asked the manager to point out five of your fastest producers,"},{"time":1130000,"text":"and then I went and looked at each one of them for about 15 or 20 minutes,"},{"time":1134000,"text":"and picked this one woman."},{"time":1136000,"text":"And it was just lightning fast;"},{"time":1138000,"text":"the way she was working was almost unbelievable."},{"time":1140000,"text":"But that is the trick that they've got right now,"},{"time":1143000,"text":"that they're winning with, is that they're using"},{"time":1146000,"text":"all the latest technologies and extrusion machines,"},{"time":1148000,"text":"and bringing all the components into play,"},{"time":1152000,"text":"but the assembly is where they're actually bringing in --"},{"time":1155000,"text":"the country workers are very willing to work. They want to work."},{"time":1160000,"text":"There's a massive backlog of people wanting their jobs."},{"time":1164000,"text":"That condition's going to be there for the next 10 to 15 years"},{"time":1167000,"text":"if they realize what they want, which is, you know,"},{"time":1170000,"text":"400 to 500 million more people coming into the cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1173000,"text":"In this particular case -- this is the assembly line that you saw;"},{"time":1176000,"text":"this is a shot of it."},{"time":1177000,"text":"I had to use a very small aperture to get the depth of field."},{"time":1180000,"text":"I had to have them freeze for 10 seconds to get this shot."},{"time":1185000,"text":"It took me five fake tries"},{"time":1188000,"text":"because they were just going. To slow them down was literally impossible."},{"time":1192000,"text":"They were just wound up doing these things all day long,"},{"time":1195000,"text":"until the manager had to, with a stern voice, say,"},{"time":1197000,"text":"\"Okay, everybody freeze.\""},{"time":1199000,"text":"It wasn't too bad,"},{"time":1202000,"text":"but they're driven to produce these things at an incredible rate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1208000,"text":"This is a textile mill doing synthetic silk, an oil byproduct."},{"time":1215000,"text":"And what you're seeing here is,"},{"time":1217000,"text":"again, one of the most state-of-the-art textile mills."},{"time":1221000,"text":"There are 500 of these machines; they're worth about 200,000 dollars each."},{"time":1224000,"text":"So you have about 12 people running this,"},{"time":1226000,"text":"and they're just inspecting it -- and they're just walking the lines."},{"time":1229000,"text":"The machines are all running,"},{"time":1231000,"text":"absolutely incredible to see what the scale of industries are."},{"time":1234000,"text":"And I started getting in further and further into the factories."},{"time":1239000,"text":"And that's a diptych. I do a lot of pairings"},{"time":1242000,"text":"to try and get the sense of scale in these places."},{"time":1245000,"text":"This is a line where they get the threads"},{"time":1247000,"text":"and they wind the threads together,"},{"time":1249000,"text":"pre-going into the textile mills."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1253000,"text":"Here's something that's far more labor-intensive,"},{"time":1255000,"text":"which is the making of shoes."},{"time":1257000,"text":"This floor has about 1,500 workers on this floor."},{"time":1262000,"text":"The company itself had about 10,000 employees,"},{"time":1266000,"text":"and they're doing domestic shoes."},{"time":1269000,"text":"It was very hard to get into the international companies"},{"time":1272000,"text":"because I had to get permission from companies like Nike and Adidas,"},{"time":1276000,"text":"and that's very hard to get."},{"time":1278000,"text":"And they don't want to let me in."},{"time":1280000,"text":"But the domestic was much easier to do."},{"time":1282000,"text":"It just gives you a sense of, again -- and that's where,"},{"time":1285000,"text":"really, the whole migration of jobs started going over to China"},{"time":1288000,"text":"and making the shoes. Nike was one of the early ones."},{"time":1291000,"text":"It was such a high labor component to it"},{"time":1296000,"text":"that it made a lot of sense to go after that labor market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1299000,"text":"This is a high-tech mobile phone: Bird mobile phone,"},{"time":1303000,"text":"one of the largest mobile makers in China."},{"time":1305000,"text":"I think mobile phone companies"},{"time":1308000,"text":"are popping up, literally, on a weekly basis,"},{"time":1312000,"text":"and they have an explosive growth in mobile phones."},{"time":1316000,"text":"This is a textile where they're doing shirts --"},{"time":1320000,"text":"Youngor, the biggest shirt factory and clothing factory in China."},{"time":1323000,"text":"And this next shot here is one of the lunchrooms."},{"time":1327000,"text":"Everything is very efficient."},{"time":1329000,"text":"While setting up this shot,"},{"time":1331000,"text":"people on average would spend eight to 10 minutes having a lunch."},{"time":1339000,"text":"This was one of the biggest factories I've ever seen."},{"time":1341000,"text":"They make coffeemakers here, the biggest coffeemaker"},{"time":1346000,"text":"and the biggest iron makers --"},{"time":1350000,"text":"they make 20 million of them in the world."},{"time":1352000,"text":"There's 21,000 employees. This one factory -- and they had several of them --"},{"time":1357000,"text":"is half a kilometer long."},{"time":1359000,"text":"These are just recently shot -- I just came back about a month ago,"},{"time":1362000,"text":"so you're the first ones to be seeing these,"},{"time":1365000,"text":"these new factory pictures I've taken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1368000,"text":"So it's taken me almost a year to gain access into these places."},{"time":1374000,"text":"The other aspect of what's happening in China"},{"time":1377000,"text":"is that there's a real need for materials there."},{"time":1380000,"text":"So a lot of the recycled materials that are collected here"},{"time":1383000,"text":"are being recycled and taken to China by ships."},{"time":1386000,"text":"That's cubed metal. This is armatures, electrical armatures,"},{"time":1390000,"text":"where they're getting the copper and the high-end steel"},{"time":1392000,"text":"from electrical motors out, and recycling them."},{"time":1397000,"text":"This is certainly connected to California and Silicon Valley."},{"time":1400000,"text":"But this is what happens to most of the computers."},{"time":1403000,"text":"Fifty percent of the world's computers end up in China to be recycled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1407000,"text":"It's referred to as \"e-waste\" there."},{"time":1409000,"text":"And it is a bit of a problem. The way they recycle the boards"},{"time":1413000,"text":"is that they actually use the coal briquettes,"},{"time":1416000,"text":"which are used all through China, but they heat up the boards,"},{"time":1419000,"text":"and with pairs of pliers they pull off all the components."},{"time":1422000,"text":"They're trying to get all the valued metals out of those components."},{"time":1425000,"text":"But the toxic smells -- when you come into a town"},{"time":1428000,"text":"that's actually doing this kind of burning of the boards,"},{"time":1431000,"text":"you can smell it a good five or 10 kilometers before you get there."},{"time":1434000,"text":"Here's another operation. It's all cottage industries,"},{"time":1437000,"text":"so it's not big places -- it's all in people's front porches,"},{"time":1442000,"text":"in their backyards, even in their homes they're burning boards,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1448000,"text":"if there's a concern for somebody coming by --"},{"time":1451000,"text":"because it is considered in China to be illegal, doing it,"},{"time":1454000,"text":"but they can't stop the product from coming in."},{"time":1458000,"text":"This portrait -- I'm not usually known for portraits,"},{"time":1461000,"text":"but I couldn't resist this one, where she's been through Mao,"},{"time":1465000,"text":"and she's been through the Great Leap Forward,"},{"time":1467000,"text":"and the Cultural Revolution, and now she's sitting on her porch"},{"time":1470000,"text":"with this e-waste beside her. It's quite something."},{"time":1473000,"text":"This is a road where it's been shored up by computer boards"},{"time":1477000,"text":"in one of the biggest towns where they're recycling."},{"time":1480000,"text":"So that's the photographs that I wanted to show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1484000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1486000,"text":"I want to dedicate my wishes to my two girls."},{"time":1488000,"text":"They've been sitting on my shoulder the whole time while I've been thinking."},{"time":1491000,"text":"One's Megan, the one of the right, and Katja there."},{"time":1494000,"text":"And to me the whole notion --"},{"time":1496000,"text":"the things I'm photographing are out of a great concern"},{"time":1498000,"text":"about the scale of our progress and what we call progress."},{"time":1503000,"text":"And as much as there are great things around the corner --"},{"time":1506000,"text":"and it's palpable in this room --"},{"time":1509000,"text":"of all of the things that are just about to break"},{"time":1511000,"text":"that can solve so many problems,"},{"time":1514000,"text":"I'm really hoping that those things will spread around the world"},{"time":1517000,"text":"and will start to have a positive effect."},{"time":1520000,"text":"And it isn't something that isn't just affecting our world,"},{"time":1522000,"text":"but it starts to go up -- because I think we can start correcting"},{"time":1525000,"text":"our footprint and bring it down -- but there's a growing footprint"},{"time":1530000,"text":"that's happening in Asia, and is growing at a rapid, rapid rate,"},{"time":1534000,"text":"and so I don't think we can equalize it. So ultimately the strategy,"},{"time":1539000,"text":"I think, here is that we have to be very concerned about their evolution,"},{"time":1543000,"text":"because it is going to be connected to our evolution as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1547000,"text":"So part of my thinking, and part of my wishes,"},{"time":1550000,"text":"is sitting with these thoughts in mind,"},{"time":1553000,"text":"and thinking about,"},{"time":1555000,"text":"\"How is their life going to be when they want to have children,"},{"time":1558000,"text":"or when they're ready to get married 20 years from now -- or whatever,"},{"time":1561000,"text":"15 years from now?\""},{"time":1563000,"text":"And to me that has been the core behind most of my thinking --"},{"time":1566000,"text":"in my work, and also for this incredible chance to have some wishes."},{"time":1574000,"text":"Wish one: world-changing. I want to use my images"},{"time":1578000,"text":"to persuade millions of people to join in the global conversation on sustainability."},{"time":1583000,"text":"And it is through communications today"},{"time":1586000,"text":"that I believe that that is not an unreal idea."},{"time":1590000,"text":"Oh, and I went in search -- I wanted to put what I had in mind,"},{"time":1594000,"text":"hitch it onto something. I didn't want a wish just to start from nowhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1598000,"text":"One of them I'm starting from almost nothing, but the other one,"},{"time":1601000,"text":"I wanted to find out what's going on that's working right now."},{"time":1604000,"text":"And Worldchanging.com is a fantastic blog, and that blog"},{"time":1612000,"text":"is now being visited by close to half-a-million people a month."},{"time":1617000,"text":"And it just started about 14 months ago."},{"time":1622000,"text":"And the beauty of what's going on there"},{"time":1624000,"text":"is that the tone of the conversation is the tone that I like."},{"time":1630000,"text":"What they're doing there is that they're not --"},{"time":1633000,"text":"I think the environmental movement has failed"},{"time":1636000,"text":"in that it's used the stick too much;"},{"time":1638000,"text":"it's used the apocalyptic tone too much;"},{"time":1641000,"text":"it hasn't sold the positive aspects of"},{"time":1646000,"text":"being environmentally concerned and trying to pull us out."},{"time":1649000,"text":"Whereas this conversation that is going on in this blog"},{"time":1652000,"text":"is about positive movements,"},{"time":1655000,"text":"about how to change our world in a better way, quickly."},{"time":1658000,"text":"And it's looking at technology, and it's looking at new energy-saving devices,"},{"time":1663000,"text":"and it's looking at how to rethink and how to re-strategize"},{"time":1667000,"text":"the movement towards sustainability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1670000,"text":"And so for me, one of the things that I thought"},{"time":1674000,"text":"would be to put some of my work in the service of promoting"},{"time":1680000,"text":"the Worldchanging.com website."},{"time":1683000,"text":"Some of you might know, he's a TEDster -- Stephen Sagmeister and I"},{"time":1688000,"text":"are working on some layouts. And this is still in preliminary stages;"},{"time":1692000,"text":"these aren't the finals. But these images, with Worldchanging.com,"},{"time":1698000,"text":"can be placed into any kind of media."},{"time":1700000,"text":"They could be posted through the Web;"},{"time":1703000,"text":"they could be used as a billboard or a bus shelter, or anything of that nature."},{"time":1710000,"text":"So we're looking at this as trying to build out."},{"time":1714000,"text":"And what we ended up discussing"},{"time":1716000,"text":"was that in most media you get mostly an image with a lot of text,"},{"time":1721000,"text":"and the text is blasted all over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1723000,"text":"What was unusual, according to Stephen,"},{"time":1725000,"text":"is less than five percent of ads are actually leading with image."},{"time":1730000,"text":"And so in this case,"},{"time":1732000,"text":"because it's about a lot of these images and what they represent,"},{"time":1735000,"text":"and the kinds of questions they bring up,"},{"time":1737000,"text":"that we thought letting the images play out and bring someone to say,"},{"time":1742000,"text":"\"Well, what's Worldchanging.com, with these images, have to do?\""},{"time":1747000,"text":"And hopefully inspire people to go to that website."},{"time":1751000,"text":"So Worldchanging.com, and building that blog, and it is a blog,"},{"time":1755000,"text":"and I'm hoping that it isn't -- I don't see it as the kind of blog"},{"time":1758000,"text":"where we're all going to follow each other to death."},{"time":1760000,"text":"This one is one that will spoke out, and will go out,"},{"time":1763000,"text":"and to start reaching. Because right now there's conversations"},{"time":1766000,"text":"in India, in China, in South America --"},{"time":1768000,"text":"there's entries coming from all around the world."},{"time":1771000,"text":"I think there's a chance to have a dialogue, a conversation"},{"time":1774000,"text":"about sustainability at Worldchanging.com."},{"time":1777000,"text":"And anything that you can do to promote that would be fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1782000,"text":"Wish two is more of the bottom-up, ground-up one that I'm trying to work with."},{"time":1785000,"text":"And this one is: I wish to launch a groundbreaking competition"},{"time":1789000,"text":"that motivates kids to invest ideas on, and invent ideas on, sustainability."},{"time":1796000,"text":"And one of the things that came out --"},{"time":1798000,"text":"Allison, who actually nominated me, said something earlier on"},{"time":1801000,"text":"in a brainstorming. She said that recycling in Canada"},{"time":1804000,"text":"had a fantastic entry into our psyche through kids between grade four and six."},{"time":1812000,"text":"And you think about it, you know,"},{"time":1814000,"text":"grade four -- my wife and I, we say age seven is the age of reason,"},{"time":1818000,"text":"so they're into the age of reason. And they're pre-puberty."},{"time":1822000,"text":"So it's this great window where they actually are --"},{"time":1824000,"text":"you can influence them. You know what happens at puberty?"},{"time":1827000,"text":"You know, we know that from earlier presentations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1830000,"text":"So my thinking here is that we try to motivate those kids"},{"time":1837000,"text":"to start driving home ideas. Let them understand what sustainability is,"},{"time":1841000,"text":"and that they have a vested interest in it to happen."},{"time":1843000,"text":"And one of the ways I thought of doing it is to use my prize,"},{"time":1848000,"text":"so I would take 30,000 or 40,000 dollars of the winnings,"},{"time":1852000,"text":"and the rest is going to be to manage this project,"},{"time":1854000,"text":"but to use that as prizes for kids to get into their hands."},{"time":1857000,"text":"But the other thing that I thought would be fantastic"},{"time":1859000,"text":"was to create these -- call them \"prize targets.\""},{"time":1863000,"text":"And so one could be for the best sustainable idea"},{"time":1867000,"text":"for an in-school project, the best one for a household project,"},{"time":1872000,"text":"or it could be the best community project for sustainability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1875000,"text":"And I also thought there should be a nice prize"},{"time":1878000,"text":"for the best artwork for \"In My World.\" And what would happen --"},{"time":1882000,"text":"it's a scalable thing. And if we can get people to put in things --"},{"time":1887000,"text":"whether it's equipment, like a media lab,"},{"time":1889000,"text":"or money to make the prize significant enough --"},{"time":1891000,"text":"and to open it up to all the schools that are public schools,"},{"time":1896000,"text":"or schools that are with kids that age,"},{"time":1898000,"text":"and make it a wide-open competition for them"},{"time":1901000,"text":"to go after those prizes and to submit them."},{"time":1903000,"text":"And the prize has to be a verifiable thing, so it's not about just ideas."},{"time":1908000,"text":"The art pieces are about the ideas and how they present them"},{"time":1911000,"text":"and do them, but the actual things have to be verifiable."},{"time":1914000,"text":"In that way, what's happening is that"},{"time":1916000,"text":"we're motivating a certain age group to start thinking."},{"time":1919000,"text":"And they're going to push that up, from the bottom -- up into,"},{"time":1924000,"text":"I believe, into the households. And parents will be reacting to it,"},{"time":1928000,"text":"and trying to help them with the projects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1930000,"text":"And I think it starts to motivate the whole idea towards sustainability"},{"time":1934000,"text":"in a very positive way,"},{"time":1936000,"text":"and starts to teach them. They know about recycling now,"},{"time":1939000,"text":"but they don't really, I think, get sustainability in all the things,"},{"time":1942000,"text":"and the energy footprint, and how that matters."},{"time":1945000,"text":"And to teach them, to me, would be a fantastic wish,"},{"time":1949000,"text":"and it would be something that I would certainly put my shoulder into."},{"time":1954000,"text":"And again, in \"In My World,\" the competition --"},{"time":1956000,"text":"we would use the artwork that comes in from that competition to promote it."},{"time":1960000,"text":"And I like the words, \"in my world,\""},{"time":1962000,"text":"because it gives possession of the world to the person who's doing it."},{"time":1965000,"text":"It is my world; it's not someone else's. I want to help it;"},{"time":1968000,"text":"I want to do something with it. So I think it has a great opportunity"},{"time":1973000,"text":"to engage the imaginations -- and great ideas, I think, come from kids --"},{"time":1978000,"text":"and engage their imagination into a project,"},{"time":1980000,"text":"and do something for schools."},{"time":1982000,"text":"I think all schools could use extra equipment, extra cash --"},{"time":1985000,"text":"it's going to be an incentive for them to do that."},{"time":1989000,"text":"And these are some of the ideas in terms of where"},{"time":1992000,"text":"we could possibly put in some promotion for \"In My World.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1998000,"text":"And wish three is: Imax film. So I was told I should do one for myself,"},{"time":2004000,"text":"and I've always wanted to actually get involved with doing something."},{"time":2008000,"text":"And the scale of my work, and the kinds of ideas I'm playing with --"},{"time":2011000,"text":"when I first saw an Imax film, I almost immediately thought,"},{"time":2014000,"text":"\"There's a real resonance between what I'm trying to do"},{"time":2016000,"text":"and the scale of what I try to do as a photographer.\""},{"time":2019000,"text":"And I think there's a real possibility"},{"time":2023000,"text":"to reach new audiences if I had a chance."},{"time":2025000,"text":"So I'm looking, really, for a mentor, because I just had my birthday."},{"time":2029000,"text":"I'm 50, and I don't have time to go back to school right now --"},{"time":2032000,"text":"I'm too busy. So I need somebody"},{"time":2034000,"text":"who can put me on a quick catch-up course on how to do something like that,"},{"time":2039000,"text":"and lead me through the maze of how one does something like this."},{"time":2043000,"text":"That would be fantastic. So those are my three wishes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2046000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}